ul.li:
(15) A silicone rubber-based hardening composition containing:
linear organopolysiloxane having a vinyl group (A);
linear organohydrogen polysiloxane (B);
silica filler (C) of which the surface is treated with a silane coupling agent having a trimethylsilyl group; and
silica filler (D) of which the surface is treated with a silane coupling agent having an organosilyl group containing a vinyl group.
